---
title: Double Chicken & Creamy Peppercorn Sauce with Mash & Veggies
description: One taste of this creamy peppercorn sauce and you'll want to slather it on everything! The gentle heat melds beautifully with the decadent
cream for a rich and tasty addition to this simple meal. Add some mash and nutty greens for a weeknight dinner that's better than most!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-creamy-peppercorn-sauce-ed2707e3.jpg
